<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>fù xìng de shí kè yǐ jīng lái dào 迦南137</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 fù xìng de shí kè yǐ jīng lái dào, yǔ shuǐ zhǐ zhù, dōng tiān yǐ wǎng,
 bǎi niǎo míng jiào, wàn wù dōu sū xǐng, fù xìng de shí kè lái dào le,
 zhè gè shì dài shǔ yú yé sū, zhè gè shí dài shǔ yú wǒ men,
 gāo jǔ dà qí zhěng zhuāng dài fā zhāo jù gè guó gè fāng gè zú de rén lái.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>137</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
</song>